data.description: This exquisite single-family two-story home offers 5 bedrooms and 3 full baths, providing ample space for comfortable living. With walk-in closets in every room, an open concept design, and a fenced yard with a covered patio, this home is perfect for indoor-outdoor entertaining, privacy and security. The spacious master suite includes a sitting area, master bath with double vanity, separate shower, and a large soaking tub, creating a serene retreat. A bedroom and full bathroom on the main level offer convenience, while the separate dining area adds elegance to meals. The kitchen features granite countertops, a breakfast bar, walk-in pantry, and modern appliances for culinary enthusiasts. Upstairs, the owner's suite and three additional bedrooms, all with huge walk-in closets, provide privacy and comfort. The laundry area is conveniently located upstairs for added convenience. Plus, residents can enjoy community amenities such as swimming pools, tennis courts, a covered picnic pavilion, and clubhouse, making every day feel like a vacation. This single-family two-story home features a practical two-car garage, providing convenient parking and storage space for residents.
